What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take it, but only if you are really interesting in the subject and willing to put in the time to read the papers. By far the most valuable part of the class for me was reading the papers, and the class is structured so that you could easily get away without reading them.
Yes, if you are interested in the subject matter.
Definitely, but be prepared to put in some of your time to go beyond the readings and really grasp the essential.
